fact WorkItem(
  id: "WI-135",
  description: "Proposal 030 phase ε.4 — soundness boundary + implementation-status documentation. Update docs/proposals/030-theorem-registry.md with: (a) §Implementation status — landed sub-phases with commit refs, deferred items; (b) §Soundness boundary — explicit list of trust base components (Z3 for SmtDischarge replay; kernel re-reading source for ScopeAxiom; structural composition check for Specialization; user-asserted trust for TrustedAxiom); (c) update §Open questions to mark Variant 3 (WI-119) resolved for provides; (d) brief lifecycle note that prove writes sidecars, check reads them. Acceptance: docs review only — no code changes.",
